subject: ANN: test your JUnit 3.8/4.0 skills
msgSnippet: JavaBlackBelt announces two new exams on JUnit: You can take a free exam on JUnit 3.8
messageBody:
JavaBlackBelt announces two new exams on JUnit:

You can take a free exam on JUnit
3.8
(http://javablackbelt.com/jbb/QuestionnaireDefDisplay.do?questpublicId=00148)
or JUnit 4.0
(http://javablackbelt.com/jbb/QuestionnaireDefDisplay.do;1142192192231?questpublicId=00118.)


The JUnit 3.8 exam tests your basic JUnit knowledge. It can count
towards a Java belt.

The JUnit 4.0 covers the new/different features in JUnit 4.0. You can
take it as often as you like, so it is a good way to practice/review
JUnit 4.0.
